{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074020/extras/context01_en.jpg?t=1739246159\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u3010Real and authentic CRPG\u3011</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Online, a unique adventure game! Each character has a distinctive image and skills, with unique styles of movements. Players can work together to encircle powerful fantasy legendary creatures, obtain fantasy ingredients, cook your own unique dishes, and gain unique abilities and skills!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u3010 Rich gameplay \u3011</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Here, you can freely explore, collect, team up dungeons, challenge, hunt, fish, set up stalls, upgrade, strengthen, treasure hunt, make, dress up, make headwear, clothes, and other interesting gameplay. (All content is world dropped/created, and transactions are also completed or initiated by players independently)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Of course, you can also return to the main gameplay at any time. (Find the NPC dialogue that continues the main storyline, and you can start the main storyline journey again)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Regarding the inheritance of mainline attributes: Every time the mainline is opened, it will be inherited into the current mainline task based on the strength and equipment of the character in the big world. That is to say, the stronger the character, the higher the initial attribute skills of the character each time the main storyline is opened.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u3010Gorgeous Battle\u3011</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can gain many different abilities by cooking food and eating different dishes. Flexibly using them is an indispensable aid for your adventure journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074020/extras/615x334.jpg?t=1739246159\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.stea